Description:
Live in or Invest - 584m2
This lovely 3 bedroom home in Corio is ready for you to move into! Perfect for first home buyers or investors alike. Upon entry, there is a lovely tiled loungeroom, leading through to the dining room and kitchen. The 3 carpeted bedrooms all have built in robes. At the end of the driveway, there is a remote roller door leading through to the backyard with a large concrete area for additional off street parking, with double garage and spacious backyard. This property has the potential as a development site (STCA). Current rental estimate $300 per week. This property won't last long at this price!

Description:
Family Living In Cloverdale Estate
Set in the very popular Cloverdale Estate is this neat & tidy family home. Featuring 3 good sized bedrooms, an updated kitchen with gas cooking, dishwasher and separate dining area. Large L-shaped lounge room with a wood fire. Large outdoor entertaining area for all-year-round entertaining and a large back yard plus a single lock up Colorbond garage and ample off-street parking. Currently tenanted with fantastic tenants paying $295/week until April 2019. Set within walking distance to schools, kindergartens, shops & public transport at your doorstep only a few minutes from Geelong Ring Rd & Princes Hwy for Geelong/Surf Coast and Melbourne Commuting.

A set and forget investment.

Outside is a perfect area to soak up the morning sun in the gorgeous and private backyard. The front of the property is low maintenance with graveled area, great for extra off-street parking. There is also secure fencing at the front which includes a single carport and double lock up garage.
Other features include: Gas wall furnace, 2 x air-conditioners, linen cupboard and plenty of storage.
Easy access to both the Princess Highway/Melbourne Road and the Princess Freeway means just a 10 minute drive to Geelong's CBD and also ideally located for Melbourne commuters. The home is located close to public transport.
Packed full of potential this comfortable family home is one not to be missed.

Description:
Unique opportunity in prime location.
This delightful well-lit home is one that will ignite your excitement. Immaculately presented with a charming neutral colour scheme and functional floor plan. Designed for easy living, this low maintenance residence boasts comfort and style that will delight all home buyers and investors alike! Boasting a large comfortable lounge upon entry with gas heating, air conditioning and a built in bar. Following through to the well equipped kitchen with gas cooking and ample cupboards overlooking the meals area. Three bedrooms in total are located down the hallway adjacent the family bathroom with separate shower and bath tub. The rear yard provides a wonderful undercover decked alfresco that runs right down the rear of the allotment and opens to a grassed area with side access for additional parking. Connected to the SLUG lies an additional fourth bedroom or rumpus room complete with split system air conditioning. Brilliantly located in a well-established neighbourhood within walking distance to Banksia reserve, public transport, schools for all ages and Goldsworthy convenience store. With only a 2 minute drive to both Bell Post and Corio shopping centre as well as the Ring road all major amenities are within easy reach. Neat as a pin this ideal brick veneer home is a must see.
